#React Basics
- React is a library , which can work inside a function too.
- With React we can create full fledged app with the help of bundler and other packages
- installing react from CDN
  - with cdn link , network call happen when script encounters, unlike node modules
  - after package downloaded , it will be available on browser so no need to import react in ur js
  - 
- JS module 
  - pure JS does not understand import export so we have to pass type="module" to script
- Creating React element
- Creating ReactDOM root
- intializing git repo
